data.description: **Lake Front with private dock.**Enjoy all the amenities and security within the gated community of Lake Seven Falls at the low cost HOA of $250 per year which includes trash service, water supply, road maintenance and public access to  stocked lakes and ponds, picnic pavilions, beach, boat ramp and ATV trails!! Natural Elements give this home a rustic charm with a cozy cabin feel. A large deck and yard with a beautiful lake view are great for entertaining or just a morning cup of joe. The partially finished full walkout basement is packed with possibilities. With open floor plan, hard wood floors, newer roof, fireplace, vaulted ceilings and cedar paneling through out this one is a rare find and won't last long!!
